      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "There is now a proposed BIP standardizing a process for setting up multisignature wallets - https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/1097\r\nAlso a proposed BIP for an updated hierarchy for cosigners in multisignature wallets - https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/1089\r\n\r\nThis would include descriptor wallets, [PSBTs](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/21283), and (hopefully) [QR codes](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/9913).\r\n\r\nSomething that has also been discussed is possibly increasing the [checksum](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/descriptors.md#checksums) in the descriptor language. See discussion [here](https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/1097#issuecomment-817515315)\r\n\r\nThis would also be a significant/final part of my $1,500 bounty posted here - https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/21071",
